source: TEXT_HEAVNZ927_01992_SEQ_00<tab>The Allagan enhancement node appears agitated.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ927_01992_SEQ_00<tab>第VII転送リングの改善システムは、静かに佇んでいる。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ927_01992_SEQ_01<tab>The Allagan enhancement node informs you that several dragons have escaped from an experiment. It asks you to kill all three of these enhanced predators to negate the extreme risk they pose.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ927_01992_SEQ_01<tab>改善システムから、洗脳実験の失敗で暴走したドラゴン族を排除するよう指示された。アジス・ラーのエシュ・トーム南で「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F20FE901 /var>」を3体討伐しよう。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ927_01992_SEQ_02<tab>You eliminate the escaped specimens. All that is left is to inform the enhancement node.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ927_01992_SEQ_02<tab><var 28 ((BNpcName)) F20FE901 /var>を討伐した。第VII転送リングの「改善システム」に報告しよう。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ927_01992_SEQ_03<tab>The enhancement node thanks you for dealing with the dragons, explaining that it will review this incident and attempt to prevent its recurrence.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ927_01992_SEQ_03<tab>改善システムに報告した。兵器としての戦闘力を強化するため、凶暴性を増すように洗脳したことが暴走の原因のようだ。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ927_01992_TODO_00<tab>Slay merdragons at the designated areas.

TEXT_HEAVNZ927_01992_IMPROVEMENTSYSTEM_000_000<tab>Receiving emergency request for assistance from security division...<buzzzzzz>...catastrophic failure...<buzzzzzz>...dragon behavioral control experiment.
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ927_01992_IMPROVEMENTSYSTEM_000_000<tab>ザ……ザザ……保安部より救援要請。
ドラゴン族を制御するための洗脳試験で事故が発生しました。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ927_01992_IMPROVEMENTSYSTEM_000_001<tab>Multiple merdragons escaped from isolation and...<buzzzzzz>...mandate immediate termination of all three subjects to avoid possible... <buzzzzzz>
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ927_01992_IMPROVEMENTSYSTEM_000_001<tab>対象が洗脳に耐え切れず暴走し、逃亡……。
「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F20FE901 /var>」を排除願います。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ927_01992_IMPROVEMENTSYSTEM_000_010<tab><buzzzzzz> ...mandate immediate termination of all subjects to avoid...<buzzzzzz>...event. Repeat transmission. Catastrophic failure of... <buzzzzzz>
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ927_01992_IMPROVEMENTSYSTEM_000_010<tab>対象が洗脳に耐え切れず暴走し、逃亡……。
「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F20FE901 /var>」を排除願います。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ927_01992_IMPROVEMENTSYSTEM_000_020<tab>Neutralization of subjects confirmed. The Allagan Empire thanks you for your contribution.
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ927_01992_IMPROVEMENTSYSTEM_000_020<tab>ザ……ザザ……
対象の反応消失を確認、お疲れさまでした。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ927_01992_IMPROVEMENTSYSTEM_000_021<tab>Preliminary assessment indicates test subject escape was instigated by elevated aggression levels induced as part of testing protocol. A comprehensive review will be carried out to prevent a future occurrence of similar events and assist the testing and research facility in their unwavering efforts to... <buzzzzzz>
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ927_01992_IMPROVEMENTSYSTEM_000_021<tab>兵器としての戦闘能力を強化するため、
凶暴性を増したことが、今回の事故に繋がった模様……。
さらなる改善を……ザザ……完全な兵器に……ザ……。
